    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "[?",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "It-- ?] it was in-- in east Poland.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "[?",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "We ?] was thinking-- we start to form something, and was thinking that-- we [? can-- ?] we got some help.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "And all of a sudden, we see the help.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "Start to came the Russian army.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "We don't know [? that ?] they got a treaty between Poland-- between Germany and Russia, because they divided Poland to the Bug, to this River Bug.",
      "word_count": 27
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "We don't know nothing.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And all of a sudden we were thinking, can help?",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And this not what's help.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "This is Russian army, and they give us plenty fire.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "[LAUGHS] The planes came, the Russian planes, bombard us.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "I run away like a crazy, throw away everything, and I run.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "It's a one story.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "[LAUGHS] [?",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "This story. ?]",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I run to hide someplace.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "So I run to the place, they call this-- a small place.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "It's a-- it's a Jewish shtetl called [NON-ENGLISH].",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "So I run over there, and I hiding in some places over there.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "I find some Jewish, and they hide me in some-- in some place, and I stay over there hiding.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "So when I--",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yeah, I throw it away.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Throw away everything-- my arms, everything [? junk. ?] [LAUGHS] Not so-- I'm not no more a soldier, not so nothing.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And I stay over there for a time being.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And then I see through the holes where they hide me, I see is coming the army, the Russian army coming and coming.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "For day and night they walking, day and night.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "We all [INAUDIBLE].",
